Rating: 4
Unbelievably easy recipe. Fantastic flavor. We all but finished it off throughout the day. I used a previous review's suggestion of substituting 1/2 cup maple syrup for a 1/2 cup of the milk. We then didn't need to top it w/syrup. A MUST MAKE recipe.

Rating: 4
This is the most awesome breakfast recipe I have ever made! However, I made the following changes/substitutions: Substitute maple sausage for the regular sausage (I used Johnsonville), and substitute pure maple syrup for some of the milk (I think I used 1/2 cup). I made this for our daughter's baptismal party and it was devoured in less than 10 minutes! I didn't even get to try it the first time! Enjoy!

