Rating: 4
I have made Fench Toast in this style for years. Thick slices of French Bread, same egg/milk combo and I bake it in the oven til brown. This is a great way to do breakfast. The strata can be breakfast on the go!

Rating: 0
To the cook below, please do not steer clear of stratas as a result of this recipe. They are wonderful choices for brunches because it's so easy to prepare them in advance and just pop them in the oven. A lot has to do with your bread choice and the amount of liquid it soaks up. I haven't tried this recipe yet, so I don't know if perhaps the portions are off. But try the sausage, cheddar, and vegetable strata or the spinach and grueyere strata from this site - you might change your mind on stratas. Think of them as a cross between an omelet and savory bread pudding.

